headline.main: Rangers Continue to Roll With Rout of the Canucks

snippet: Kevin Hayes and J.T. Miller scored two goals each, and Henrik Lundqvist registered 36 saves as the Rangers recorded their eight win in their last nine games....
lead_paragraph: Kevin Hayes and J.T. Miller scored two goals each, and Henrik Lundqvist registered 36 saves as the Rangers recorded their eight win in their last nine games.
